<h3 align="center">General Information</h3>

<p>Haxathon 2012 is a continuous CTF-style game where participants obtain 
points by completing challenges. The game is always available and never
ends.</p>

<p>This game is played on a private VPN and you must be invited to play this 
CTF.</p>

<h3 align="center">Rules</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>All players play individually.</strong>
        This is not a team exercise. No cooperation between players is allowed.
        Specifically academic faculty, other players and
        irc.freenode.net#rainbowsandpwnies are not acceptable sources of aid.
        Other non-affiliated IRC channels/forums are <em>OK</em> to receive help
        from.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>No DOSing services or modifying the game</strong> in a manner
        which disrupts other players' ability to play. If you need a challenge
        reset, contact an organizer.
    </li>
    <li>
        Attacking other players and stealing flags from other players is OK and
        generally accepted <em>to the extent allowed by the law</em>.
    </li>
</ul>
